    "description": "Woo demons or angels in this paranormal romance adventure. Side with Chaos or with Order. Uncover the truth, save the kid, and tame the hellhound. Brimstone Manor is a world of secrets. Magic. Miracles. And a battle between Heaven and Hell… a battle for your heart. <br><br>Your new home is riddled with secrets, from its forbidden basement to a family dog straight out of Hell. Can you survive being a demon’s nanny? When sparks fly, will you fall for the hunky angel or your mysterious, demonic boss?<br><br><i>Brimstone Manor</i> is a 152,000-word interactive novel by Frances Pauli. It's entirely text-based, without graphics or sound effects, and fueled by the vast, unstoppable power of your imagination.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Play as male, female, or non-binary; gay, straight, or poly.<br></li><li> Choose your love interest.<br></li><li> Learn magic.<br></li><li> Work miracles.<br></li><li> Tame the hellhound.<br></li><li> Fly!<br></li><li> Befriend or defeat the terrifying demoness.<br></li><li> Reveal the truth to the world or keep the paranormal a secret.</li></ul><br>Defend the demon’s mansion, protect his kid, and discover your heart’s desire.",
